1)
Illustrative landscaping plan, showing landscaped areas, buffers, typical cross-sections,
and any special landscape features. A more specific and detailed plan and schedule shall
be submitted as part of the Site Plan required for approval of a Special Exception Permit;
m) A typical dwelling unit location plan including a siting of individual dwelling units in
